Class SimpleRatingPredictor.Provider

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.grouplens.lenskit.basic.SimpleRatingPredictor.Provider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.inject.Provider<RatingPredictor>
    Enclosing class:
    SimpleRatingPredictor

    public static class SimpleRatingPredictor.Provider
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.inject.Provider<RatingPredictor>

    An intelligent provider for simple rating predictors. It provides a simple rating predictor if there are an ItemScorer and UserEventDAO available, and returns null otherwise. This is the default provider for RatingPredictor.
